metadata.name: Lunatic Unrevealed
metadata.description: The LUNATICS is a genesis collection of 777 fine art NFTs minted from the artwork of renowned contemporary artist Christopher Lizarraga. Your LUNATIC gives you access to a fine art collective of influential artists and NFT drops like no other digital collectible, including IRL art giveaways, holders-only raffles, unique collector experiences with influential artists and much more to discover on the LUNATICS roadmap. For more information, visit lunaticsnft.xyz.
